file.content:
---
openapi: 3.0.2
servers:
  - description: test
    url: https://example.org/api
info:
  title: Test
  version: 1.0
paths:
  /test:
    get:
      summary: get
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string
    patch:
      summary: patch
      requestBody:
        content:
          text/plain:
            schema:
              type: string
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
  /foo:
    get:
      summary: get foo
      responses:
        '200':
          description: OK
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: string

Error: json: cannot unmarshal number into Go struct field Info.info.version of type string
